{"tid":1200838,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣] 中國提名「禿鷹」曾偉雄出任聯合國總幹事，作為香港人我哋應該關注","createTime":"2019-06-11T00:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T00:45:47.000Z","uid":159913,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4468910f1d62581421e42fa43ed55e9d82a17707","tid":1200838,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:08:30.000Z","msg":"事件簡介: <br />\n國家禁毒委副主任、香港前警務處長曾偉雄獲中國政府提名競聘聯合國駐維也納辦事處總幹事兼聯合國毒品和犯罪問題辦公室執行主任。<br />\n<br />\n總部設於美國紐約的聯合國，分別在奧地利維也納、瑞士日內瓦和肯尼亞內羅畢設立3個辦事處，<span style=\"color: red;\">其中維也納辦事處負責協調國際原子能機構、聯合國工業發展組織等相關機構。聯合國毒品和犯罪問題辦公室，則專責執行聯合國在全球禁毒、滅罪、反腐敗和打擊恐怖活動的工作。</span>兩個機構由同一名主管領導。<br />\n<br />\n明報source: <a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/y3dkek4v\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fy3dkek4v&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lS8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=55d02579\" target=\"_blank\">https://tinyurl.com/y3dkek4v</a><br />\n<br />\n曾偉雄做咗咁耐警務處處長，做得好唔好香港人有目共睹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為國際公民我哋好應該關注吓聯合國總幹事候任人選，表達吓我哋意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論支持反對都好，我覺得要有理有據，可以由以下主題入手，配合返UN嘅job requirement表達<br />\n1. 侵害人權<br />\n2. 警隊紀律問題<br />\n3. 妨礙新聞自由<br />\n<br />\n到底曾偉雄係咪一個有偏見(固執、唔靈活)嘅人呢?<br />\n到底曾偉雄能唔能夠同唔同國家嘅人跨界別合作?<br />\n如果曾偉雄嘅過往紀錄唔符合UN嘅宗旨同份工嘅要求，咁我覺得佢in完應該返屋企等電話囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾偉雄小cv:<br />\n香港警務處處長(公職): 2011-2015<br />\n震雄集團(商業機構)兼職策劃顧問: 2016-?<br />\n載通國際(商業機構) 董事、審核及風險管理委員會成員:2018-?<br />\n中共国家禁毒委员会副主任(共職): 2019-<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞(值得留意外媒對佢嘅評價):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3013117/ex-hong-kong-police-chief-andy-tsang-wai-hung-nominated-lead-un-agency\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F3013117%2Fex-hong-kong-police-chief-andy-tsang-wai-hung-nominated-lead-un-agency&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lS8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=401696b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3013117/ex-hong-kong-police-chief-andy-tsang-wai-hung-nominated-lead-un-agency</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-06-05/china-nominates-occupy-era-police-chief-for-un-post-scmp-says\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-06-05%2Fchina-nominates-occupy-era-police-chief-for-un-post-scmp-says&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lS8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=044d5528\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-06-05/china-nominates-occupy-era-police-chief-for-un-post-scmp-says</a>"},{"pid":"e334e502177b3e000dca7e48f8f6bf1018f3a749","tid":1200838,"uid":120913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4468910f1d62581421e42fa43ed55e9d82a17707","tid":1200838,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:08:30.000Z","msg":"事件簡介: <br />\n國家禁毒委副主任、香港前警務處長曾偉雄獲中國政府提名競聘聯合國駐維也納辦事處總幹事兼聯合國毒品和犯罪問題辦公室執行主任。<br />\n<br />\n總部設於美國紐約的聯合國，分別在奧地利維也納、瑞士日內瓦和肯尼亞內羅畢設立3個辦事處，<span style=\"color: red;\">其中維也納辦事處負責協調國際原子能機構、聯合國工業發展組織等相關機構。聯合國毒品和犯罪問題辦公室，則專責執行聯合國在全球禁毒、滅罪、反腐敗和打擊恐怖活動的工作。</span>兩個機構由同一名主管領導。<br />\n<br />\n明報source: <a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/y3dkek4v\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fy3dkek4v&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lS8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=55d02579\" target=\"_blank\">https://tinyurl.com/y3dkek4v</a><br />\n<br />\n曾偉雄做咗咁耐警務處處長，做得好唔好香港人有目共睹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為國際公民我哋好應該關注吓聯合國總幹事候任人選，表達吓我哋意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論支持反對都好，我覺得要有理有據，可以由以下主題入手，配合返UN嘅job requirement表達<br />\n1. 侵害人權<br />\n2. 警隊紀律問題<br />\n3. 妨礙新聞自由<br />\n<br />\n到底曾偉雄係咪一個有偏見(固執、唔靈活)嘅人呢?<br />\n到底曾偉雄能唔能夠同唔同國家嘅人跨界別合作?<br />\n如果曾偉雄嘅過往紀錄唔符合UN嘅宗旨同份工嘅要求，咁我覺得佢in完應該返屋企等電話囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾偉雄小cv:<br />\n香港警務處處長(公職): 2011-2015<br />\n震雄集團(商業機構)兼職策劃顧問: 2016-?<br />\n載通國際(商業機構) 董事、審核及風險管理委員會成員:2018-?<br />\n中共国家禁毒委员会副主任(共職): 2019-<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞(值得留意外媒對佢嘅評價):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3013117/ex-hong-kong-police-chief-andy-tsang-wai-hung-nominated-lead-un-agency\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F3013117%2Fex-hong-kong-police-chief-andy-tsang-wai-hung-nominated-lead-un-agency&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lS8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=401696b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3013117/ex-hong-kong-police-chief-andy-tsang-wai-hung-nominated-lead-un-agency</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-06-05/china-nominates-occupy-era-police-chief-for-un-post-scmp-says\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-06-05%2Fchina-nominates-occupy-era-police-chief-for-un-post-scmp-says&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lS8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=044d5528\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-06-05/china-nominates-occupy-era-police-chief-for-un-post-scmp-says</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:09:31.000Z","msg":"支持！<br />\n但攪左自己個單先？<br />\n我地好urgent 呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a00ef8623f6be314f04e5967ce4a161324e83a9","tid":1200838,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:13:15.000Z","msg":"其中維也納辦事處負責協調國際原子能機構、聯合國工業發展組織等相關機構。<span style=\"color: red;\">聯合國毒品和犯罪問題辦公室，則專責執行聯合國在全球禁毒、滅罪、反腐敗和打擊恐怖活動的工作。</span>兩個機構由同一名主管領導。<br />\n<br />\nbtw我查咗少少資料，<br />\n雖然唔關佢事，但佢任內嗰段時間香港廉潔程度係有改善嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吸毒率好似都係，要揀嚟報<br />\n其他資料未得閒詳細搵，要靠大家力量喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmo